(Overview) Tj
T*
(Trigonometry connects angles and side lengths in triangles using ratios such as sine,) Tj
T*
(cosine, and tangent.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of Trigonometry in Mathematics using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind right-triangle ratios and deciding which trig ratio fits) Tj
T*
(a question.) Tj
T*
